parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Front Suspension Failure (Ball Joints, Wheel Bearings, etc.)
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of front suspension components can cause the wheel to fall off, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Loud noises
vibrations
and uneven tire wear. The wheel may fold into the wheel well
causing damage and potentially leading to loss of control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cooling system can cause the engine to overheat, leading to engine damage or failure.
symptoms: Overheating
coolant leaks
and radiator failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of electrical system components can cause the vehicle to stall or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Alternator failure
battery failure
and electrical system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Performance Issues (Crank Sensor, Fuel Pump, etc.)
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of engine performance components can cause the vehicle to stall or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Engine stalling
poor engine performance
and warning lights on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Body and Frame Issues (Rust, Door Hinges, etc.)
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of body and frame components can cause structural damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: Rust
door hinge failure
and body damage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose acceleration, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or delays when shifting into gear
the transmission slips or fails to engage
the vehicle loses reverse gear
the vehicle vibrates or makes a grinding noise when shifting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle's gauges to malfunction, leading to a loss of control or accidents.
symptoms: The gauges on the dashboard bounce or malfunction
the brakes feel like they are engaged
the vehicle's electrical system fails to function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the four-wheel drive system can cause the vehicle to lose traction, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The four-wheel drive system fails to engage
the vehicle's transfer case needs to be replaced
the vehicle's four-wheel drive indicator light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ball joints can cause the vehicle's suspension to fail, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The ball joints fail prematurely
the vehicle's suspension makes a loud noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the alternator can cause the vehicle's electrical system to fail, leading to a loss of control or accidents.
symptoms: The alternator fails prematurely
the vehicle's electrical system fails to function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hazard switch can cause the brake lights and hazard lights to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The brake lights and hazard lights do not function
the brake lights are intermittent
the hazard lights do not turn off
the turn signal switch exhibits an abnormal clicking sound
the brake lights and hazard lights fail to operate when the turn signal is engaged.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake light switch can cause the brake lights to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The brake lights do not function
the brake lights are intermittent
the brake lights fail to operate when the brake pedal is depressed
the brake lights and hazard lights fail to operate when the turn signal is engaged.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the multi-function switch can cause the brake lights, hazard lights, and turn signals to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The brake lights and hazard lights do not function
the turn signal switch exhibits an abnormal clicking sound
the brake lights and hazard lights fail to operate when the turn signal is engaged
the multi-function switch smokes when the turn signal is used.
